data.description: Beautifully custom-built home Located on .93 of an acre lot in the Woodland Waters Community. The home features 4 bedrooms 3 baths, a huge bonus room with 2 closets that could be another master suite, an office with built-ins., and an oversized 3-car garage. Upon entry, you’ll enjoy the open floor plan and tall tray ceilings throughout the home.  The gourmet kitchen is equipped with a gas stove, a New refrigerator, a new dishwasher, Corian countertops, wood cabinetry, and an Island. The Kitchen overlooks the spacious family room with lots of natural light. The family room features a brick gas fireplace and, large pocket sliders that open directly to the large lanai overlooking a gorgeous screened-in saltwater pool with a waterfall. Let's not forget about the Jacuzzi! The Master bedroom has 2 walk-in closets, and the master bath has a walk-in shower. On the opposite side of the Master bedroom are the other 2 bedrooms, along with the 2nd bath. The bonus room/bedroom and 3rd bath are on the same side.   Other features include a multi-speed pool pump, Pool heater & cooler system, salt chlorine generator, Pool automation system with internet access, Pool pop-up cleaner & 4 valves actuator—mechanical water softener for the entire home. The sprinkler system is wifi ready. A new washer and dryer are included. Waze ring bell with camera, Security system with 15 sensors, and door lock. New hardwood looking ceramic tile floors in all of the bedrooms.    Located in one of the most coveted communities in Hernando County with large lots and custom homes all spaced Zoned for the county's newest schools Winding Waters K-8 and Weeki Wachee High School! Low HOA fee of under $175 a year. No flood insurance is required! Located close to shopping, restaurants, a hospital, IMAX movies, entertainment, kayaking down the clear Weeki Wachee River, State Park, Mermaid Show, and Water Park. 10 minutes to the sunset at Pine Island and 10 minutes from the Suncoast Parkway
